import { Box } from 'reflexbox'
import { Label, Input } from '@rebass/forms'


function auth(){
    return(
        <Box>
            <Label htmlFor='email'>Email</Label>
                <Input
                    id='email'
                    name='email'
                    type='email'
                    placeholder='jane@example.com'
                />
                <Input
                    id='password'
                    name='password'
                    type='password'
                    placeholder='password'
                />
        </Box>
    )
}

export default auth
